Title: Space
Plot: A mysterious force is sabotaging a space launch program, which leads directly back to the commander of the team who once led a mission to Mars and claimed to have seen an alien in space.
GuestStars: Ed Lauter, Susanna Thompson, Tom McBeath, Terry David Mulligan, Tyronne L'Hirondelle, Norma Wick, Alfred E. Humphreys, David Cameron, French Tickner, Paul Desroches
